      "content": "# Requirement Verification Questions\n\nUse this document to validate the requirements gathered during the inception phase.\nFill in each answer directly in the docs viewer and save.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Scope & Goals\n\n**What is the primary goal of this migration?**\n\n[Answer]: Migrate all functionalities to local cloud based framework\n\n---\n\n**Which existing integrations are mandatory to keep (ComfyUI, Ollama, MySQL)?**\n\n[Answer]: All of them\n\n---\n\n## 2. Infrastructure\n\n**Which local AWS services (via floci.io) are approved for use?**\n\n[Answer]: S3, RDS, Cloudfront, SQS, SNS, DynamoDB, Api Gateway v2, IAM, STS, Secret Manager, Step Functions, ECS\n\n---\n\n**What is the expected deployment environment (OS, RAM, GPU)?**\n\n[Answer]: WIndows, 32GB RAM, 16GB VRAM\n\n---\n\n## 3. Constraints\n\n**Are there hard deadlines or budget constraints for this migration?**\n\n[Answer]: No\n\n---\n\n**What is the acceptable downtime during the migration?**\n\n[Answer]: Are no users active at this time, only testers users for validation. Downtime is acceptable in any scale\n"
