      "section": "reverse-engineering",
      "content": "# Dependencias\n\n## Dependencias Internas\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    AppPy[\"app.py\"] --> Factory[\"app/__init__.py\"]\n    AppPy --> DB[\"services/db.py\"]\n    AppPy --> Gallery[\"gallery/routes.py\"]\n    AppPy --> Media[\"services/media_store.py\"]\n\n    Factory --> Core[\"core/routes.py\"]\n    Factory --> Gallery\n    Factory --> Generation[\"generation/routes.py\"]\n    Factory --> Video[\"video/routes.py\"]\n    Factory --> Chat[\"chat/routes.py\"]\n    Factory --> Workflow[\"workflow_editor/routes.py\"]\n\n    Core --> Comfy[\"services/comfyui.py\"]\n    Core --> DB\n    Core --> Paths[\"services/workflow_paths.py\"]\n\n    Gallery --> Cache[\"services/image_cache.py\"]\n    Gallery --> Media\n    Gallery --> DB\n\n    Generation --> Comfy\n    Generation --> Media\n    Generation --> DB\n\n    Video --> Comfy\n    Video --> Media\n\n    Chat --> Media\n    Chat --> DB\n\n    Workflow --> DB\n    Workflow --> Paths\n```\n\n## Relacoes Internas Principais\n\n### `app.py` depende de `app/__init__.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: precisa criar a instancia Flask.\n\n### `app.py` depende de `app/services/db.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: aplica schema e seeds no startup.\n\n### Blueprints dependem de `app/services/comfyui.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: submeter workflows, fazer polling e uploads.\n\n### Blueprints dependem de `app/services/media_store.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: ler e persistir catalogos de midia, galerias e relacionamentos.\n\n### Blueprints dependem de `app/services/db.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: settings, conexao SQL e catalogos transacionais.\n\n### `app/services/comfyui.py` depende de `app/services/workflow_paths.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: localizar arquivos de workflow do ComfyUI.\n\n### `app/services/image_cache.py` depende de `config.py`\n\n- **Type**: Runtime.\n- **Reason**: acessar caminhos montados e TTL de atualizacao.\n\n## Dependencias Externas\n\n### `flask`\n\n- **Version**: nao fixada no repositorio.\n- **Purpose**: framework web principal.\n- **License**: BSD-3-Clause.\n\n### `werkzeug`\n\n- **Version**: nao fixada no repositorio.\n- **Purpose**: request/response helpers e seguranca de nomes de arquivos.\n- **License**: BSD-3-Clause.\n\n### `requests`\n\n- **Version**: nao fixada no repositorio.\n- **Purpose**: consumo de APIs HTTP externas.\n- **License**: Apache-2.0.\n\n### `psutil`\n\n- **Version**: nao fixada no repositorio.\n- **Purpose**: metricas de CPU e memoria no agente de stats.\n- **License**: BSD-3-Clause.\n\n### `opencv-python-headless`\n\n- **Version**: nao fixada no repositorio.\n- **Purpose**: thumbnails de video no backend.\n- **License**: Apache-2.0.\n\n### `PyMySQL`\n\n- **Version**: `>=1.1.0`.\n- **Purpose**: acesso ao MySQL 8.\n- **License**: MIT.\n\n### `mysql:8`\n\n- **Version**: 8.x via imagem Docker.\n- **Purpose**: banco de dados operacional.\n- **License**: GPLv2 com FOSS License Exception.\n\n### `nginx:alpine`\n\n- **Version**: tag rolling Alpine.\n- **Purpose**: proxy reverso local e terminacao TLS.\n- **License**: BSD-2-Clause.\n"
